                                        <div style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:10px;"><strong>Notice:</strong><br /><em>Following the GProCongress for Pastoral Trainers in June 2016, the GProCommission seeks to capture in statistical form the number of pastors being trained around the world by various pastoral training organizations and institutions, churches, and individuals.<br />
